[09:34] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'it\'s basically a small add-on to a large AI model that teaches it one specific thing without touching the actual model itself. So when you add this to a model, it\'ll know exactly what that specific thing looks like. So let\'s say we give'

[09:47] [scene:talk]
