[10:52] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'moment. Now the inside process looks kind of like this. The LoRA adds a tiny number of weights to the diffusion model and trains these until the modified model understands the concept. So basically, it adds noise to the image and then asks the model with the LoRA to'

[11:05] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'guess what noise was added. Based on response, it knows how wrong it was and then it adjusts its answers over time to make better and better predictions. Now after that, it sends the corrections to change the LoRA by a tiny step until'

[11:17] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
